    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "<!-- deep-review-sentinel -->\n\n<!-- coder-agents-review-bot-begin -->\n**Chat:** Review in progress | [View chat](https://dev.coder.com/agents/23ec0355-fa42-4246-a7c2-a2a4d5288af1)\n**Requested:** 2026-06-09 21:48 UTC by @jscottmiller\n\n<!-- coder-agents-review-bot-end -->\n\n<!-- deep-review-begin -->\n<!-- dr-header-begin -->\n**deep-review** v0.7.1 | Round 1 | [`f95f5e6..bfb6122`](https://github.com/coder/coder/compare/f95f5e6f865fb32efeb59a62c81cbce776799850...bfb6122dd4d6f0c5fd70379e978c39586ea844a2)\n<!-- dr-header-end -->\n<!-- dr-status-begin -->\n<!-- dr-status-end -->\n<!-- dr-posted-begin -->\n**Last posted:** Round 1, 8 findings (1 P3, 2 P4, 5 Nit), COMMENT. [Review](https://github.com/coder/coder/pull/26199#pullrequestreview-4462857087)\n<!-- dr-posted-end -->\n<!-- dr-inventory-begin -->\n<details>\n<summary>Finding inventory</summary>\n\n## Findings\n\n| # | Sev | Status | Location | Summary | Round | Reviewer | Posted |\n|---|-----|--------|----------|---------|-------|----------|--------|\n| CRF-1 | P3 | Open | conn.go:148 | No test for write-failure path in Close() | R1 | Bisky P3, Chopper P3, Hisoka P3, Kite P3, Mafuuu P3, Meruem P3 | Yes |\n| CRF-2 | P4 | Open | conn.go:177 | forceClose timer starts after blocking conn.Close(), total may exceed budget | R1 | Meruem | Yes |\n| CRF-3 | P4 | Open | conn.go:95 | Close() requires active reader to complete; undocumented contract | R1 | Meruem P4, Hisoka Note | Yes |\n| CRF-4 | Nit | Open | conn.go:174 | forceClose doc omits error return on timeout path | R1 | Leorio | Yes |\n| CRF-5 | Nit | Open | conn.go:27 | forceCloseReadTimeout (const) vs readWaitTimeout (field) naming inconsistency | R1 | Gon | Yes |\n| CRF-6 | Nit | Open | conn.go:29 | Magic number 5*time.Second in waitCloseTimeout formula | R1 | Gon | Yes |\n| CRF-7 | Nit | Open | conn_internal_test.go:21 | ignoreClose field name misleading; reads ignore close, not Close itself | R1 | Gon | Yes |\n| CRF-8 | Nit | Open | conn_internal_test.go:72 | waitDone reimplements testutil.TryReceive | R1 | Robin | Yes |\n\n## Round log\n\n### Round 1\nPanel. 1 P3, 2 P4, 4 Nit. Reviewed against f95f5e6f..bfb6122dd4d6.\n\n</details>\n<!-- dr-inventory-end -->\n<!-- dr-about-begin -->\n<details>\n<summary>About deep-review</summary>\n\n**CRF** = Coder Review Finding (P0-P4, Nit, Note)\n\n| Reviewer | Focus |\n|----------|-------|\n| Bisky | tests |\n| Chopper | ops/errors |\n| Churn-guard | change verification |\n| Ging | language modernization |\n| Gon | naming |\n| Hisoka | edge cases |\n| Killua | perf |\n| Kite | change integrity |\n| Knov | contracts |\n| Knuckle | SQL |\n| Kurapika | security |\n| Law | decomposition |\n| Leorio | docs |\n| Luffy | product |\n| Mafu-san | process |\n| Mafuuu | contracts |\n| Melody | dispatch/pairing |\n| Meruem | structural |\n| Nami | frontend |\n| Netero | mechanical checks |\n| Pariston | premise testing |\n| Pen-botter | product gaps |\n| Razor | verification |\n| Robin | duplication |\n| Ryosuke | Go arch |\n| Takumi | concurrency |\n| Zoro | shape |\n\n</details>\n<!-- dr-about-end -->\n<!-- deep-review-end -->\n\n> \ud83e\udd16 Managed by [Coder Agents](https://coder.com).",
